page.title: 20VICTORIAN WEEKEND:COMPILERS
page.content: In the{Victorian Weekend,}in September the residents of Kirkby dress in Victorian costume and walk in the streets reliving past times.For tourists there are sideshows, craft demonstrations and entertainments. {Compilers:}Alison Briggs,Julie Davison Katherine Hale,Rachel Higson,Jane Mortimer,Victoria Robinson,Wendy Woods David Harrison,Iain Murry,John Power, Diane Hayton,Sally Heaton,Lee Bailes, Alison Littler,Alice Roth,Lauren Watts Rowan Whittaker,Steven Begley,Chris. Bonson,Jonathan Roch,David Smyth,Ruth Beavis,Sarah Benefield,Joanne Bowie, Catriona Matchett,Jill Robinson, Rebecca Scrase,Michael Parrott,Hans Georgeson,Steven Holcroft,Chris.
